        </tbody>
    </table>
</div>
</p>
<p>Now add <code>base.html.twig</code> in <code>Resources/views</code>. Let's steal again from the
Standard Edition. Find <code>app/Resources/views/base.html.twig</code>, copy it, and paste it
in ours:</p>
