	                                <p>Hey Alexander!</p><p>Try clearing your cache - with a "rm -rf cache/*".</p><p>Let me know if that works. I think there might be a slight bug, where you need to clear the cache ONE time after creating your first template in the Resources directory (the Symfony standard edition doesn't have this problem since you start with a Resources directory).</p><p>Cheers!</p>
